{"data": [{"id": "4741663", "title": "Old CEO Out, 'New CEO' In - Struggling Intel Is A Bargain Nonetheless", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Intel Headquarters\" data-id=\"1831946092\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">hapabapa</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><span class=\"highlighted_text\">In my last few articles about Intel Corporation (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/INTC\" title=\"Intel Corporation\">INTC</a></span>) (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NEOE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/INTC:CA\" title=\"Intel Corporation\">INTC:CA</a></span>), I was always</span> bullish, and I don\u2019t want to justify myself here in any way. I was clearly wrong about Intel in the last few quarters and obviously too optimistic about Intel</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741663-intel-stock-bargain-despite-ceo-retirement", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 11:47:50"}, {"id": "4741670", "title": "Office CMBS Delinquency Rate Spikes To 10.4%, Just Below Worst Of Financial Crisis Meltdown", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150724195/image_1150724195.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Reverse mortgage application form, financial concept\" data-id=\"1150724195\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150724195/image_1150724195.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150724195/image_1150724195.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150724195/image_1150724195.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150724195/image_1150724195.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150724195/image_1150724195.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150724195/image_1150724195.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150724195/image_1150724195.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150724195/image_1150724195.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Casper1774Studio/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>Office-to-residential conversions are growing, but are minuscule because not many towers are suitable for conversion.</em></p> <p>The delinquency rate of office mortgages that have been securitized into commercial mortgage-backed securities (CMBS) spiked by a full percentage point in November</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150724195/image_1150724195.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741670-office-cmbs-delinquency-rate-spikes-to-10-4-percent-just-below-worst-of-financial-crisis-meltdown", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 11:40:00"}, {"id": "4741660", "title": "Semrush: Strong Growth, But Risks Loom Large", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1300930633/image_1300930633.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Search Engine Optimization (SEO) Concept On Computer Screen With Two Businesswomen In The Office\" data-id=\"1300930633\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1300930633/image_1300930633.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1300930633/image_1300930633.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1300930633/image_1300930633.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1300930633/image_1300930633.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1300930633/image_1300930633.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1300930633/image_1300930633.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1300930633/image_1300930633.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1300930633/image_1300930633.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">ilkercelik</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>If you're in marketing-or just dabbling in digital-chances are you've heard of <span></span>Semrush Holdings (NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SEMR\">SEMR</a>). It's the go-to for SEO pros, the Swiss Army knife of tools, really. Keywords, backlinks, competitor data-you name it, <span></span>Semrush has it</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1300930633/image_1300930633.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741660-semrush-strong-growth-but-risks-loom-large", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 11:35:52"}, {"id": "4741659", "title": "LNG Shipping Stocks: An Uncertain Future Amid Spot Rate Pressures", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172675458/image_2172675458.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Tanker LNG FSRU Toscana Livorno, IMO 9253284, kotv\u00edc\u00ed v p\u0159\u00edstavu Janov\" data-id=\"2172675458\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172675458/image_2172675458.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172675458/image_2172675458.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172675458/image_2172675458.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172675458/image_2172675458.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172675458/image_2172675458.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172675458/image_2172675458.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172675458/image_2172675458.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172675458/image_2172675458.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Zigmunds Dizgalvis/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>UPI &amp; SPX</h2> <p>Last week, the UP World LNG Shipping Index (UPI), which tracks listed LNG shipping companies, lost 4.18 points, equivalent to 2.50%, closing at 163.40 points. The S&amp;P 500 index gained 1.06%. The chart below illustrates the performance of both</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172675458/image_2172675458.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741659-lng-shipping-stocks-uncertain-future-amid-spot-rates-pressures", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 11:30:16"}, {"id": "4741657", "title": "Cool Company: Still Cool Despite The Dividend Cut", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159343342/image_2159343342.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Digitally Generated Image of LNG Tanker Navigating Coastal Waters Representing Maritime Energy Transport\" data-id=\"2159343342\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"845px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159343342/image_2159343342.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159343342/image_2159343342.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159343342/image_2159343342.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159343342/image_2159343342.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159343342/image_2159343342.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159343342/image_2159343342.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159343342/image_2159343342.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159343342/image_2159343342.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">alvarez</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong>Note:</strong> I previously <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4725369-cool-company-my-favorite-lng-stock-as-income-generator\">covered</a> Cool Company (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CLCO\" title=\"Cool Company Ltd.\">CLCO</a></span>) in October 2024. The company has a quality fleet, robust financials, and a balanced dividend policy. At the time of publication, CLCO traded at 77% PNAV. I gave it a Strong Buy.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159343342/image_2159343342.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741657-cool-company-still-cool-despite-the-dividend-cut", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 11:24:20"}, {"id": "4741655", "title": "Liberty Energy: Return Of 'Drill, Baby Drill?' A Great Opportunity", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.s