urn-of-drill-baby-drill-a-great-opportunity", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 11:15:11"}, {"id": "4741665", "title": "Introducing The S&P Quality FCF Aristocrats Indices", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/469565348/image_469565348.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Standard &amp; Poors in NY\" data-id=\"469565348\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5302px\" height=\"3535px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/469565348/image_469565348.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/469565348/image_469565348.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/469565348/image_469565348.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/469565348/image_469565348.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/469565348/image_469565348.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/469565348/image_469565348.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/469565348/image_469565348.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/469565348/image_469565348.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">mixmotive</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Elizabeth Bebb</em></p> <p>The S&amp;P Quality Free Cash Flow (FCF) Aristocrats Indices measure companies that consistently generate robust FCF over many years. FCF, the cash remaining after a business covers its operational costs and capital investments, is crucial because it provides financial flexibility. Companies with</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/469565348/image_469565348.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741665-sp-quality-fcf-aristocrats-indices", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 11:10:00"}, {"id": "4741650", "title": "Verizon Has Ominous Clouds On The Horizon (Technical Analysis)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1339907231/image_1339907231.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Wide shot of field of mature wheat with storm clouds overhead on summer evening\" data-id=\"1339907231\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1339907231/image_1339907231.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1339907231/image_1339907231.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1339907231/image_1339907231.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1339907231/image_1339907231.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1339907231/image_1339907231.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1339907231/image_1339907231.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1339907231/image_1339907231.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1339907231/image_1339907231.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Thomas Barwick</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Thesis</h2